nodes.text: Sky Rowing was a sport. The Gaalt Sky Rowing team from the Gaalt system was a notable team.

Sky Rowing was mentioned in a profile for Skreen, a character featured in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
